    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Newark</placeName>
                <date>Sept 29<hi rend="sup">th</hi>
                    <hi rend="underline">1854</hi></date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Mr. I. Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir!</p>
            <p>Owing to you an answer of your last you will<lb/> excuse me for the detention up to
                day, I had no<lb/>
                <sic>succsess</sic> yet for more <sic>supscribers</sic> next week I shall<lb/> call
                if you wish for what is due and send it on to you, please write some more plain
                as<lb/> can't very well make <sic>outt</sic> all.</p>
            <p>We had <sic>I</sic> fine and large audience last <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> and been
                obligent to next liberty stall<lb/> for services. Our President gave us a good<lb/>
                <sic>Lectur</sic> which I will <sic>sent</sic> you too.</p>
            <p><sic>for</sic> our lot we have <sic>payd</sic> and now we<lb/> like to build but
                money we have not<lb/> and our sources are <sic>exhuastet</sic> that is<lb/> we
                    poor<add>?</add> our members are mechanics<lb/> mostly can't <sic>mak</sic> more
                    <sic>then</sic> their<lb/> living. We will address you for writing<lb/> a letter
                to represent to all congregation.<lb/> in <placeName>N. J.</placeName> and wish
                Persons for assistance<lb/> and have it <sic>printet</sic> in english &amp;
                german.<lb/> with you reference <persName>Mr. Isaacs</persName> &amp;
                    <persName>Raphael</persName>.<lb/> I hope this will bring us some <add>?</add>
                to</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>build which is the greatest want for<lb/> our <add>Hebrew</add> after our Election I
                shall give the<lb/> names from the Trustee</p>
            <p>Wishing you well I remain <sic>Respectfull</sic></p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">your servant</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <persName role="author">Joseph Cohen</persName>
            </p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
